# Demo for `kit lineup` (table) + `kit lineup --tree` (tree).
# Render with: vhs vhs/lineup.tape  → produces vhs/lineup.gif

Output vhs/lineup.gif

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Theme "ayu_light"
Set Padding 24
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

Type "kit lineup"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "kit lineup --tree"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 5s
